"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/8fb1b6/f/800x0/http://m.metrohk.com.hk/media/2012/news/2012-08-19/20120819230805ade47b50gw1dw22j53h64j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F8fb1b6%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fm.metrohk.com.hk%2Fmedia%2F2012%2Fnews%2F2012-08-19%2F20120819230805ade47b50gw1dw22j53h64j.jpg&h=d20bd17d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:13:50.000Z","msg":"就係等依張<br />\n仲有張係D領導人用Canon<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大陸仔同韓仔根本一個祖先"},{"pid":"e9f06ff407cb9e632f9359e43b8431ff47e97cc5","tid":1324330,"uid":204356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:15:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">柒</span></span>"},{"pid":"de3b3f406b1611d856aa3b126bf804c6e04aa796","tid":1324330,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:16:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02105d6c4c592eb56cde09dbe96a931e4ddba37c","tid":1324330,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:17:39.000Z","msg":"韓文支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5511c4238511f29783b024eadc19e81880c6bc0a","tid":1324330,"uid":66113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:22:11.000Z","msg":"工聯會陸頒雄發表「貿易戰、撐國貨」的貼文，稱若要打贏貿易戰，國人就要「自強不息，堅持自主創新，撐起優質國貨」。自稱攝影愛好者的他，分享一款由國產鏡廠老蛙（Laowa）生產、價值約3000元的超廣角鏡頭，指「這枝L字頭品牌的MTF 7.5mm F2 超廣角，可謂一絕，連日本原廠也做不到如此輕巧的大光圈」，又呼籲網民「有乜靚國貨可以介紹俾我」。 <br />\n<br />\n網民於貼子下留言，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">指陸頌雄曾使用日本牌子的相機</span></span>，又說為何他不穿李寧牌衣服。陸頌雄其後留言指，全球已經一體化，「撐國貨即是撐自己人」，支持民族品牌發展越來越好，但用不着罷買。<br />\n<br />\n唔怪得似陳相識啦"},{"pid":"28a0f7bfaef058341a25c87cbcf84bd448a66c27","tid":1324330,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:22:13.000Z","msg":"我突然FF呢場是代理人戰爭：韓狗(支那)，日本(美國)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}